\leftline{\bf Figure Captions}

\vskip 1truecm

{\parindent=2truecm

\litem{Figure 1:}
The integration contour used in the derivation of (3.8).  To know
the  field  $\phi$  at the point  $P$ one has  to specify  either
$\phi$ and $\dot \phi$ on $AB$ (Cauchy problem) or $\phi$ on $AC$
{\sl and} $CB$ (CIVP).  Data outside  the characteristic  cone of
$P$ need not be specified\ref{14, 23}.

\vskip 1truecm


